  <brief_title>Plasma Concentrations of Bupivacaine After Peri-articular Injection in Total Knee Arthroplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Plasma Concentrations of Bupivacaine After Spinal Anesthesia With Single Shot Femoral Nerve Block and Peri-articular Injection in Total Knee Arthroplasty</official_title>
